OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FConvicted surgeon Ian Paterson, who
OL,8,Fwas responsible for conducting
OL,9,Funnecessary surgeries on hundreds of
OL,10,Fpatients, has declined to participate
OL,11,Fin ongoing inquest hearings at
OL,12,FBirmingham Coroner's Court.
OL,14,FThe court is investigating the deaths
OL,15,Fof patients who may have suffered as a
OL,16,Fresult of Paterson's rogue medical
OL,17,Fpractices.
