OL,3,CIan Paterson declines to take part in
OL,4,Cinquests, citing health and legal
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FPaterson is currently serving a 20-
OL,8,Fyear prison sentence after being found
OL,9,Fto have carried out unnecessary and
OL,10,Funapproved procedures on more than a
OL,11,Fthousand breast cancer patients over a
OL,12,Fperiod of around 14 years.
OL,14,FPaterson, 64, was employed by the
OL,15,FHeart of England NHS Foundation Trust
OL,16,Fand practiced in the independent
OL,17,Fsector at Spire Parkway and Spire
OL,18,FLittle Aston in Birmingham.
