OL,3,CIan Paterson declines to take part in
OL,4,Cinquests, citing health and legal
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FAt 11pm last night (9th October),
OL,8,FPaterson's legal representatives
OL,9,Fapplied to revoke the Section 5 notice
OL,10,Fthat summoned him to give evidence,
OL,11,Fciting three key reasons.
OL,13,FPaterson's representatives expressed
OL,14,Fthat his attendance in court would
OL,15,Fpose a risk to his health, though the
OL,16,Fspecific nature of these concerns was
OL,17,Fnot detailed.
