OL,7,FPaterson's legal team argued that he
OL,8,Fhad not had adequate time or
OL,9,Ffacilities to properly prepare for the
OL,10,Fhearings.
OL,12,FThey emphasised that they are working
OL,13,Fon a timetable that is "days, or
OL,14,Fweeks" behind the proceedings, making
OL,15,Fit impossible to represent Paterson
OL,16,Feffectively under the current schedule.
