OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FIt was noted that Paterson does not
OL,8,Fhave proper access to disclosed
OL,9,Fmaterials and has struggled with
OL,10,Flimited facilities to meet with his
OL,11,Flegal team.
OL,13,FHis current location in a closed
OL,14,Fprison has hindered his ability to
OL,15,Fprepare for the hearings, though a
OL,16,Fpotential move to an open prison might
OL,17,Falleviate these issues.
