OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,FDespite efforts by prison authorities
OL,8,Fto facilitate Paterson's
OL,9,Fparticipation, he has ultimately
OL,10,Fdeclined to attend.
OL,12,FHis legal team reiterated that while
OL,13,FPaterson does wish to participate in
OL,14,Fthe inquest, his current circumstances
OL,15,Fmake it "unfeasible."
OL,17,FA letter to the Coroner stated:
