OL,3,CIan Paterson declines to take part in
OL,4,Cinquests, citing health and legal
OL,5,Cconcerns
OL,7,F"There is no prospect of his legal
OL,8,Frepresentatives having adequate time
OL,9,Fand facilities to prepare for the
OL,10,Fhearing as currently timetabled.
OL,12,F"In effect, proper legal
OL,13,Frepresentation is still not available
OL,14,Fto him.
OL,16,F"In the circumstances that currently
OL,17,Fprevail, it would be unreasonable to
OL,18,Fask Mr Paterson to comply with the
OL,19,FSchedule 5 Notice (the witness
OL,20,Fsummons)".
